summary: What She Says: I’m fine. What She Means: Pepperony (Pepper Potts/Tony Stark) was the first ship of the MCU and the only ship...
body:
What She Says: I’m fine.

What She Means: Pepperony (Pepper Potts/Tony Stark) was the first ship of the MCU and the only ship from Phase One to survive and it’s been sailing for a (drama filled) literal decade and if Marvel doesn’t finally let them have a happy ending in Avengers 4 after 10 soon to be 11 years I don’t think I will have the strength to emotionally invest in another ship ever again.

title: Born Again
body:
read it on the AO3 at https://ift.tt/2zb3zfe

by Nvos

Thanos the Mad Titan has been defeated, the Snap undone. The Avengers are celebrated as the greatest heroes of their time. But their victory rings hollow for the newly coronated King of Asgard, for his kingdom is one of ghosts. A mysterious magpie sent from another world seeks to help him, and in doing so, may have damned as much as he has saved.
